    <title>卡尔马克思杯思路讲解与代码</title>
    <link href="/2022/11/01/%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E9%A9%AC%E5%85%8B%E6%80%9D%E6%9D%AF%E8%A7%A3%E9%A2%98%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/"/>
    <url>/2022/11/01/%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%94%E9%A9%AC%E5%85%8B%E6%80%9D%E6%9D%AF%E8%A7%A3%E9%A2%98%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="解题过程思路"><a href="#解题过程思路" class="headerlink" title="解题过程思路"></a>解题过程思路</h3><p>  众所周知软件都会发生数据包的，通过抓包分析了下他的页面逻辑。</p><p>  发现两个请求协议都是get而且来自不同的IP，且都是由客户端发起的请求。</p><p>  具体过程简单讲解一下。客户端发送请求到前端服务器获取前端含题目等资源，完成题目后，客户端发送请求携带题号和答案返回给后端数据。</p><h4 id="麻烦的地方来了"><a href="#麻烦的地方来了" class="headerlink" title="麻烦的地方来了"></a>麻烦的地方来了</h4><p>  后端的防御措施，通过测试发现有时间戳，还有rid，唯一的一次性识别码。</p><p>紧接着我想到一件事情，前端页面有个叫做无状态的东西。</p><p>通过上述分析，我做出一个大胆的猜测，这两个API可能后端API是外包的项目，而且他们前后端的耦合程度几乎为零。</p><p>再大胆猜测一下，后端只校验题目正确性，分数的加减，记录个人信息。</p><h4 id="验证时间"><a href="#验证时间" class="headerlink" title="验证时间"></a>验证时间</h4><p>找个账号分别获取三个题型（为了校验服务器是否对题型有校验工作）而且为正确答案的数据包，向后端发送请求拿到三个回答机会，按顺序上传，发送结束答题请求后发现分数为1.5，可见后端不做题型的校验。</p><p>有人说你这个只是页面给你的数据不是真的修改，TCP长连接下回不断接受后端所发送的数据，在最后请求分数的时候可见1.5分，那说明这个猜测不成立了。</p><p>我们到现在就可以验证，后端服务器真的只做了我上述所说的那些事情。</p><p>那么就是编写代码，和获取160道题目和答案。</p><h3 id="具体解题思路"><a href="#具体解题思路" class="headerlink" title="具体解题思路"></a>具体解题思路</h3><p>python的mitmproxy的工具包，对特定请求过滤在做注入操作。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">from</span> mitmproxy <span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> http,ctx<br><span class="hljs-keyword">import</span> json<br><br><br><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Mask</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-comment"># 捕获客户端请求并修改</span><br><span class="hljs-meta">    @staticmethod</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">request</span>(<span class="hljs-params">flow: http.HTTPFlow</span>) -&gt; <span class="hljs-literal">None</span>:<br>        catchhttp = <span class="hljs-string">&quot;所要捕获url的特征信息&quot;</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> catchhttp <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> flow.request.url:<br>            data = []<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">open</span>(mode=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;r+&quot;</span>, file=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;答案路径&quot;</span>, encoding=<span class="hljs-string">&quot;utf-8&quot;</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">as</span> f:<br>                data = json.load(f)<br>                i = <span class="hljs-number">0</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> i <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">range</span>(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>, <span class="hljs-number">161</span>):<br>                    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;use&#x27;</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">not</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span> data[i].keys():<br>                        <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span><br>                data[i][<span class="hljs-string">&quot;use&quot;</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>                f.seek(<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>                f.truncate()<br>                f.write(json.dumps(data, ensure_ascii=<span class="hljs-literal">False</span>))<br><br>            flow.request.query.set_all(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;questionId&quot;</span>, [data[i][<span class="hljs-string">&quot;id&quot;</span>]])<br>            flow.request.query.set_all(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;result&quot;</span>, [data[i][<span class="hljs-string">&quot;result&quot;</span>]])<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span>:<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span><br><br><br>addons = [<br>    Mask()<br>]<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这个工具实在是没有很好的思路，利用文件的删改去实现一个全局变量的功能。</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
